 and highlighting the differences between it and the Masoretic text, each difference is explained in a brief note in an apparatus at the bottom of the page. Where expansion is appropriate, the reader is referred to extended notes at the end of the edition."--Publisher's website.00aBible.pPentateuchlSamaritan. 0aSamaritan Hebrew languagexGrammar.1 aTal, Abraham,eauthor.2 aUniversity of Cambridge.bFaculty of Asian and Middle Eastern Studies.2 aOpen Book Publishers,epublisher. 0aSemitic languages and cultures ;vv. 30.x2632-691440uhttps://doi.org/10.11647/OBP.0415zConnect to e-book42uhttps://cdn.openbookpublishers.com/covers/10.11647/obp.0415.jpgzConnect to cover image06095nam a2200433 i 99101717066580896620250313114125.0m#####o##d########cr||n|||||||||250207t20252025enkad   sb    001 0 eng d  z9781805112556 (hbk.)  z9781805112549 (pbk.)  a9781805112563q(pdf)  a9781805112594q(HTML)  a9781805112570q(EPUB)  a(OCoLC)1493375436  aStSaULbengerda 4aNavigating our way to solutions in marine conservationh[electronic resource]  /cedited by Larry B. Crowder ; assistant editor, Gabriella Stanchina. 1aCambridge :bOpen Book Publishers,c[2025] 4c©2025  a1 online resource (viii, 336 pages) :b93 illustrations, 4 tables.  atextbtxt2rdacontent  acomputerbc2rdamedia  aonline resourcebcr2rdacarrier  aAvailable through Open Book Publishers.  aOpen access resource providing free access.  aMode of access: World Wide Web.  aThis work is licensed under a Creative Commons Attribution-NonCommercial NoDerivatives 4.0 International (CC BY-NC-ND 4.0) license. For more detailed information consult the publisher's website.  aAdditional resources available from the publisher's website.  aIncludes bibliographical references and index.0 aNavigating our way to solutions in marine conservation: An introduction / Larry B. Crowder -- 1. Conserving penguins via land and sea protection / Pablo Garcia Borboroglu, Laura M.